## 5. 컴포넌트

### 5.1 버튼

**스타일: 둥근 모서리 (Rounded Corners)**

```css
/* Primary Button */
.btn-primary {
  background-color: #18b4ad;
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 1rem;
  transition: all 200ms ease-out;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
